{"tid":704002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辱罵法官法算唔算違反言論自由?","createTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:06:47.000Z","uid":47359,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c8b44daee497c9ac1fbc05b6437672d191fb00","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"點解法官有特權?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪大撚哂?"},{"pid":"658092c353de53028f44616b02b403544383faf4","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180518/large/1526608871_89b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180518%2Flarge%2F1526608871_89b3.jpg&h=1ba169fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">姓名：彭寶琴（洋名Anthea）<br />\n<br />\n年齡：56歲<br />\n<br />\n資歷：<br />\n1985年在香港大學取得社會科學學士學位，1993年通過英國曼徹斯特城市大學的法律專業共同試，翌年在港獲認許為大律師。<br />\n1995年加入律政署出任檢察官， 在民事法律科下的民事訴訟組工作；3年後晉升為高級政府律師，被調派至刑事檢控科，其後在基本法、人權、 投訴警察、淫褻物品及賭博組工作，並於2001年考取香港大學法學碩士學位。<br />\n2007年晉升為副首席政府律師，2010年獲委任為區域法院法官，2013年11月15日獲委任為高等法院原訟法庭法官至今。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">婚姻狀況：<br />\n亡夫歐陽國基生前為水警總區總部（行政）警司，2016年底疑因隱性心臟病突發在鯉景灣住所猝死，彭當時身在外地，由歐陽的水警同袍登門揭發事故。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曾審理案件：<br />\n東方明珠石油前副主席劉夢熊涉串謀詐騙案；開埠首宗無屍體無法證無招認的謀殺案重審、最終被告陳文琛仍謀殺罪成等。 <br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58206669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58206669&d=Xss1rbCGGQoh133a3dErLEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=49888aee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F58206669&h=4e9ac260\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180518/58206669</a>"},{"pid":"3c78268540789d041e9779d6e9adc96163c5f331","tid":704002,"uid":65764,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c1c8b44daee497c9ac1fbc05b6437672d191fb00","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"點解法官有特權?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪大撚哂?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"你係咪想問「禁止辱罵法官法算唔算違反言論自由」？<br />\n<br />\n答：當然違反言論自由。"},{"pid":"9b9fbe5d7c5b2645f3b1b61ee4356741c7fd0aa1","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c78268540789d041e9779d6e9adc96163c5f331","tid":704002,"uid":65764,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c1c8b44daee497c9ac1fbc05b6437672d191fb00","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"點解法官有特權?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪大撚哂?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"你係咪想問「禁止辱罵法官法算唔算違反言論自由」？<br />\n<br />\n答：當然違反言論自由。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"法律撚講下有冇得入稟嘅可能?<br />\n我知釋法大哂"},{"pid":"e649c555bf23381374d6fa515e4bbbb1fa70e880","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8c9166aa2232fc87665956d6262a07bbb6ce9f","tid":704002,"uid":65764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9fbe5d7c5b2645f3b1b61ee4356741c7fd0aa1","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c78268540789d041e9779d6e9adc96163c5f331","tid":704002,"uid":65764,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c1c8b44daee497c9ac1fbc05b6437672d191fb00","tid":704002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"點解法官有特權?<img src=\"/asse